-- Greek Deal Cuts Risk of Broad Europe Crisis, Sweden’s Borg Says
-- B y   J o h a n   C a r l s t r o m
-- 2012-02-21T11:53:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/greek-deal-cuts-risk-of-broad-europe-crisis-sweden-s-borg-says.html
Agreement on a second bailout
package for  Greece  has reduced the risk of a broad European
financial crisis, Swedish Finance Minister Anders Borg said.  This Greek accord also lessens risks in the Swedish economy
“rather significantly,” Borg told  Sveriges Radio  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Johan Carlstrom in Stockholm at 
